text: Nagaraj, Nagraj or Nagaraja or Nagarajan is a male Indian given name and Indian surname. It originates in the ' 'king of the nāgas'. It is especially prevalent in southern India and northeastern parts of India. == People == === Nagaraj === Nagaraj.V (1996), Quatity Engineer at LMW U2. Coimbatore *D. R.
